{"head":{"description":"color-hex-case Specify lowercase or uppercase for hex colors. Options string: \"lower\"|\"upper\" \"lower\" The following patterns are considered…","title":"color-hex-case"},"body":"<h1 id=\"color-hex-case\"><a href=\"#color-hex-case\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>color-hex-case</h1>\n<p>Specify lowercase or uppercase for hex colors.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span> }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**        ↑\n * These hex colors */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<p><code>string</code>: <code>\"lower\"|\"upper\"</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"lower\"><a href=\"#lower\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"lower\"</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#FFF</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span>; }</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"upper\"><a href=\"#upper\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>\"upper\"</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#FFF</span>; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/color-hex-case.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-case/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-case/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/color-hex-case/index.html.a5bc3497f4ed3f2319c947d82b7d7033.json"}